<div id="review_2237063584" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2237063584" />
    <a title="Otto Lehto" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/4024817-otto-lehto"><img alt="Otto Lehto" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1349907515p2/4024817.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2237063584?book_show_action=true">Jan 14, 2018</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Otto Lehto" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Otto Lehto" href="/user/show/4024817-otto-lehto">Otto Lehto</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2237063584" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer17240653994166032574">Engaging, inspiring, earthly, funny... Epictetus can give you great insights, skills and determination to change your life for the better, even if you don&apos;t agree with everything he says. <br/><br/>The text might be old, but our life problems are pretty much the same, so the lessons feel as contemporary and relevant as ever.<br/><br/>We can&apos;t avoid pain and hardships. Even though the topics are sombre, there is entertainment value to be had from gallows humour: I was laughing out loud half of the time, and the othe</span>
  <span id="freeText17240653994166032574" style="display:none">Engaging, inspiring, earthly, funny... Epictetus can give you great insights, skills and determination to change your life for the better, even if you don't agree with everything he says. <br /><br />The text might be old, but our life problems are pretty much the same, so the lessons feel as contemporary and relevant as ever.<br /><br />We can't avoid pain and hardships. Even though the topics are sombre, there is entertainment value to be had from gallows humour: I was laughing out loud half of the time, and the other half snickering quietly.</span>
  <a data-text-id="17240653994166032574" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

