<span id="freeTextContainer2246253185772980702">An interesting read. There&apos;s a lot to think about. I found a lot of wisdom and common sense. If you find Stoic tranquility to be something worthy pursuing, definitely a good book to read. It has some datedness to some material, though.</span>
  <span id="freeText2246253185772980702" style="display:none">An interesting read. There's a lot to think about. I found a lot of wisdom and common sense. If you find Stoic tranquility to be something worthy pursuing, definitely a good book to read. It has some datedness to some material, though.</span>
